{"tid":1606321,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[出師有名][濃縮][心理準備]六區革命既目標、任務、戰略","createTime":"2019-09-30T14:03:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T04:58:50.000Z","uid":69419,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"baa6491771a02b9676511f32b05cb604a1894c24","tid":1606321,"uid":69419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:03:07.000Z","msg":"目標：<br />\n光復香港  時代革命<br />\n五大訴求  缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n任務：<br />\n請參考<br />\n十一國殤　六區開花<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1600404\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1600404</a><br />\n<br />\n戰略：<br />\n1.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yAtxDpe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyAtxDpe.jpg&h=edc8731e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一定要攝衫，唔攝當鬼處理！<br />\n<br />\n2.<br />\n每人一枝防身短棍<br />\n$12蚊店層架腳<br />\n地拖棍，鬆肉槌，款式應有盡有！<br />\n<br />\n3. <br />\n小隊同行，切勿單機！落單真係要起人先做到。<br />\n<br />\n4.<br />\n遇狗即打，黑警係我地仇人，無須留手！<br />\n手足出事，打狗救人！<br />\n組隊打波1,2,3,4,5 開波！<br />\n<br />\n5.<br />\n和勇合一<br />\n勇武為矛，和理為盾！<br />\n勇武記住和理係盾，佢地先係真坦，你應該進攻<br />\n和理記住勇武係矛，千祈唔好落單，團結既你係無敵盾<br />\n<br />\n6. <br />\n潛在焦土，如果工兵，魔法師物資足夠，將狗屋變焦土可以有效打擊對手<br />\n<br />\n7.<br />\n攻其不備，車都唔畀佢落就攻<br />\n真係對侍，起RB 之後就戰壕式推進<br />\n即係穩守》掩護》攻佔》穩守<br />\n無限輪迴<br />\nP.S. 旗兵可穩定軍心，盡多！<br />\n<br />\n8.<br />\n最後一點，都係最重要嘅一點。<br />\n永遠確保逃生路線，例如軍團式推進，留意包抄嘅可能<br />\n打完唔夠打都可以走！<br />\n<br />\n 祝各位<br />\n武運昌隆<br />\n旗開得勝"},{"pid":"7480e4bf9abaf3b360efa510273ef50781865b31","tid":1606321,"uid":69419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:05:05.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3938af3283c83308796d086e4a444ad354615b56","tid":1606321,"uid":150267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:07:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">三點燒黨旗</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">［主線］<span style=\"color: red;\">聽日一定要做啲有標誌性嘅</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1604870\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1604870</a><br />\n<br />\n勇武 和理非入<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\"> 依到有合集帶啲咩</span></strong><br />\n［整合］<span style=\"color: gold;\">十一執齊野</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1603888\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1603888</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">無豬咀就帶定條濕毛巾cover 口同鼻 <br />\n會好啲</span><br />\n<br />\n同埋唔好行甘前</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">仲有巴打目標post<br />\n十一國殤　六區開花<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1600404\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1600404</a></span>"},{"pid":"c0ad9f052034465b871f1f4e15128441c34c1a5d","tid":1606321,"uid":69419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:21:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"569581801b5c0a07a25291bd4e0bac98d6e74190","tid":1606321,"uid":69419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:22:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3cf1f89e3be067832420529b534aa3332ec46e11","tid":1606321,"uid":202228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:27:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9c9a7181ee5b7270a4daf0ff2c7848cfb50c612a","tid":1606321,"uid":267304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:29:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4N9EiEd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4N9EiEd.png&h=1efb94f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日元朗大西北巴絲小心啊 架警車入南邊圍無著紅藍燈 泊左一段時間了</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d5edf088236f080f43604a6b3469db1998b20b34","tid":1606321,"uid":77526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:36:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6097c08972ac4964ad25b5980bdd3f4e94631631","tid":1606321,"uid":276191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:39:25.000Z","msg":"可能同白衫軍夾定明天的部署"},{"pid":"b41ee43550d65302a9fc2d2919f559bce8a4